    <item>
      <title>Snapchat 将支付 1500 万美元以和解加州的骚扰诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-19/snapchat-inc-to-pay-15-million-to-settle-discrimination-and-harassment-lawsuit-in-california</link>
      <description><![CDATA[旧金山（美联社）——Snapchat 公司将支付 1500 万美元以和解加州民权机构提起的诉讼，该机构称该公司歧视女性员工、未能防止工作场所性骚扰并对投诉的女性进行报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-19/snapchat-inc-to-pay-15-million-to-settle-discrimination-and-harassment-lawsuit-in-california</guid>
